Trade/Device Name(s): Audit® MicroControls™ FD Linearity Tumor Markers II
Audit® MicroControls™M Linearity FD Tumor Markers II
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Audit® MicroControls™ FD Linearity Tumor Markers II assayed QC material for chemistry analytes simulating human samples for linearity/calibration verification.
Indications for Use Summary: In vitro diagnostic assayed quality control material intended to simulate human patient samples for use in determining linearity, calibration verification, and verification of reportable range for specified tumor marker analytes.
